No! No!

720
01:06:41,617 --> 01:06:43,505
- Throw her in!
- No! Aah!

721
01:06:43,658 --> 01:06:44,946
- Are you all right?
- I'm okay.

722
01:06:48,697 --> 01:06:49,941
Shit, they got the kid.

723
01:06:51,097 --> 01:06:52,701
- I gotta go after her.
- Go get her.

724
01:06:53,818 --> 01:06:55,585
- You stay with the police.
- Be careful.

725
01:06:55,737 --> 01:06:57,144
Damn it!

726
01:07:13,497 --> 01:07:15,383
Are you hurt, ma'am?

727
01:07:27,177 --> 01:07:28,541
Shit.

728
01:07:36,656 --> 01:07:38,096
He has a gun on me.

729
01:07:39,975 --> 01:07:41,776
Brent, he has a gun.

730
01:07:43,176 --> 01:07:44,257
Please hear me.

731
01:07:46,856 --> 01:07:48,537
<i>I hope you can see this.</i>

732
01:07:48,936 --> 01:07:50,781
Quiet! Don't talk.

733
01:07:56,777 --> 01:07:59,266
<i>Brent, I'm trying
to show you where we are.</i>

734
01:08:07,177 --> 01:08:08,617
Move out of my way!

735
01:08:15,375 --> 01:08:16,785
Brent, yes!

736
01:08:19,335 --> 01:08:20,864
- You're screwed, asshole!
- Shut up!

737
01:08:23,816 --> 01:08:25,824
Come on, come on.

738
01:08:46,137 --> 01:08:47,664
Oh!

739
01:08:57,936 --> 01:08:59,420
Damn it!

740
01:09:06,215 --> 01:09:07,982
What are you doing? Is that a camera?

741
01:09:11,496 --> 01:09:13,897
- Give it to me, give it to me!
- No, give it back!

742
01:10:03,814 --> 01:10:05,582
Ah, shit! Bastard.

743
01:10:25,095 --> 01:10:26,100
Damn it!

744
01:11:29,574 --> 01:11:30,578
Oh, shit.

745
01:12:07,653 --> 01:12:08,974
Shit.

746
01:12:37,254 --> 01:12:39,502
The only way out of the city.

747
01:12:40,374 --> 01:12:41,738
I know where she is.

748
01:13:15,493 --> 01:13:18,701
- Pull over! Give me the gun!
- What are you doing? Stop it!

749
01:13:19,333 --> 01:13:20,381
You want us to die?

750
01:13:42,972 --> 01:13:44,936
Come on, come on!

751
01:15:11,652 --> 01:15:13,256
- Get out!
- What?

752
01:15:13,812 --> 01:15:15,176
Now!

753
01:15:39,971 --> 01:15:42,099
- Are you okay? Are you okay?
- Yeah.

754
01:15:49,732 --> 01:15:52,056
Stay there.
You're under arrest.

755
01:16:06,412 --> 01:16:07,612
Thanks.

756
01:16:07,771 --> 01:16:10,215
Everybody back!

757
01:16:19,051 --> 01:16:20,132
Ugh!

758
01:16:22,531 --> 01:16:25,096
- I guess I owe you one, huh?
- And you owe me a new car.

759
01:16:25,251 --> 01:16:29,256
Don't worry about the car. It just needs
a new paint job and she'll be fine.

760
01:16:43,972 --> 01:16:46,176
- What's that?
- I don't know.

761
01:16:48,451 --> 01:16:50,011
It's not mine.

762
01:16:53,091 --> 01:16:55,655
<i>- Hello?
- Aren't you going to thank me?</i>

763
01:16:55,811 --> 01:16:58,418
<i>I did for you
what you could never do for yourself.</i>

764
01:16:58,570 --> 01:17:00,851
<i>I showed you what you are made of.</i>

765
01:17:01,492 --> 01:17:06,020
<i>Please excuse me
if I wasn't able to be there in person.</i>

766
01:17:06,851 --> 01:17:09,099
<i>I'm sure you understand,
under the circumstances...</i>

767
01:17:09,251 --> 01:17:11,575
<i>...it would have been
most inconvenient for me.</i>

768
01:17:12,450 --> 01:17:15,496
<i>If you're asking yourself
who I am to you...</i>

769
01:17:15,891 --> 01:17:20,376
<i>...I will answer very simply:
I am your greatest fan.</i>

770
01:17:21,211 --> 01:17:24,134
<i>I always thought you could have been
at the very top of your profession...</i>

771
01:17:24,291 --> 01:17:26,691
<i>...if only you believed you could.</i>

772
01:17:26,930 --> 01:17:29,331
<i>So that's it, you see.</i>

773
01:17:30,691 --> 01:17:34,979
<i>Please send your lovely wife my
best wishes for a happy Christmas.</i>

774
01:17:35,130 --> 01:17:39,331
<i>I'm sincerely glad you worked things out
to be with her for the holidays.</i>

775
01:17:41,571 --> 01:17:45,815
<i>It's the season to be together
with loved ones, so I'm told.</i>

776
01:17:46,331 --> 01:17:48,534
<i>I have very few loved ones.</i>

777
01:17:51,691 --> 01:17:55,291
<i>My consolation is I have
a lot of money.</i>

778
01:17:55,450 --> 01:17:58,855
<i>And now, quite a lot more
of it, thanks to you.</i>

779
01:17:59,570 --> 01:18:04,731
<i>I doubt if our paths will cross again,
but then, life is full of surprises.</i>

780
01:18:05,690 --> 01:18:09,017
<i>So let's just say au revoir.</i>

781
01:18:10,010 --> 01:18:13,818
<i>Be assured,
it's been most entertaining.</i>

